manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Does your baby feel bored and hate to sit on the car seat? Scream and try to get out? Don’t worry. Our high contrast black and white fox activity spiral car seat toys can help you distract baby in car seat during the long drives. Cute Animal Shape: We design the babies car seat toys in adorable fox, elephant with music box inside, hot air balloon with wind chime and crinkle paper, teether with rotatable ball, cloud with BB device. Multi-functional to keep baby busy and enjoy playing with the baby toys. High Quality Activity Plush Toys: The infant toy is made of soft PP cotton plush, fabric and soft plastic, completely comfortable and safe for newborn boy and girl aged 0-18 months to touch, squeeze, grab. Multi-Colored and Textured: With a high contrast black and white colors, mixed textures and shapes, the carseat toys for infants 0-6 months can easily catch baby’s eyes and distract baby’s attention, offer you some free time to do some things like cooking, washing, working, driving, and more.

Baby Swing Toys The black and white toys can be easily to spiral on swing, amuse baby and encourage them to lift head, perfect hanging toys for baby 0-3 months. Baby Crib Toys It's wonderful to wrap around our high contrast crib toys on the crib tails, helpful to keep baby fall into deep sleep and have fun when wake up. Baby Stroller Toys The stroller toys for baby 0 3 6 12 months can become a good friend to accompany baby when go outside for a walk or trip.

Educational Learning Toys and Parent-Child Interactive Toys for Baby 0-24 Months Include 4 Functional Devices: - Musical Elephant: Just squeeze the elephant's tummy, will automatically play a soft melody. - Teether Ball: Teehter is made of premium plastic, safe for baby to chew, and the ball is rotatable and fun. - BB Squeaker Owl: Squeeze it and will hear "bibi" sound, with a mirror on the back. - Wind Chime Hot Air Ballon: Shake the hot air ballon, baby can hear "ring ring" clear voices, with crinkle paper on the bottom. With the functional black and white toys, you can teach baby to recognize animals, tell some relevant stories or play games together to amuse baby, develop baby's brain , stimulate imagination and curiosity to the world. Baby will try to reach, pull, bat, grab, squeeze the cute animal plush toys, help to enhance their muscle strength, hand-eye coordination, develop tactile, visual and auditory sense ability. Snake design makes it easy to spiral our infant toys on car seat, stroller, crib, swing, play gym, rocker, bouncer, bassinet, or any other nursery device with handle. Allow baby to play wherever and whenever, no need to worry about baby get bored when long drive.
This hanging baby toy will be great for baby shower, birthday, Christmas gift. Perfect for baby boys and girls from 0-36 months.
